data.title: Dorm Room Space Savers - Tips to make the most out of your small space
data.description: Life isn’t into respecting boundaries, privacy, or basic social cues. And that’s readily apparent during freshman year of college. Complete opposites get hurled into a cracker box space and are left to sort out the ensuing chaos. Talk about an education! Give coeds (and anyone living in a small space) a chance, a head start, and a heads up with these tricks to help with sharing space, containing chaos, and organizing in cramped spaces.
